{"tid":1407101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(極之重要)香城online戰術post (1)","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:14:00.000Z","uid":82241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d82e209be2199bc0e75a8f1f021b32471b1c90a","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"火攻:  可攻可守<br />\n攻既 等示威者增加士氣  滅警犬氣勢<br />\n守既 等消防救火  警犬推唔到 撤退時間增加<br />\n<br />\n堵塞交通 : 可阻擋警車到場<br />\n利用其他市民車輛 窒住警犬<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有一個小小建議<br />\n就係整路障個時 留一條車路比車走<br />\n窒車之餘 市民又有得走<br />\n肯定會支持，又唔會反彈</span></span><br />\n<br />\nbe water : 有得走 又唔會比人拉<br />\n唔洗解釋啦<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人 加油</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b82b1e9c27ca6b11216fd2d3a51725524e17613b","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99eba9200b703eceec71bfd2f458f42283f5131d","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"168bf94ae7b9f21e6acd71ef62a28fa6e60416f2","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d251af486ca09fe6789efcde1206d206d52d6250","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa39411cfdfb25313804055bc6094986084f0f81","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4050fac2feda0fb1587eae3e92ae792218e3ffa9","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca3d7d8c786f521be8bb621fbf4a7c854bb3666b","tid":1407101,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T1